                        <interp inst="t18490409-name-883" type="given" value="ROBERT"></interp>ROBERT RANDALL</persName>
                  </hi>. I live in Goodman's-fields. On 20th March, about ten minutes past three o'clock, I was on Tower-hill, looking at the soldiers, and saw the prisoner take a handkerchief from a gentleman's pocket, and put it into his trowsers pocket—the gentleman walked away—I gave the prisoner in charge.</p>
