                        <interp inst="t18490409-name-884" type="given" value="WILLIAM"></interp>WILLIAM COOPER</persName>
                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">policeman, H</hi> 198). Randall pointed out the prisoner to me—he ran away, a man stopped him—I took him, and felt his pockets, bat could find no handkerchief—he said he had not taken no handkerchief—we had not walked many yards before it came out at the bottom of his trowsers—he said at the station a man gave it him.</p>
